('5578679940', 'terms_of_service', 'Introduction', '<p><span style="font-family: ''courier new'', courier;">Last modified: January 3, 2014</span></p>\r\n<h4>Introduction</h4>\r\n<p>Welcome to Zidoff.com. Zidoff E-Commerce Limited and/or its affiliates ("Zidoff") provide website features and other products and services to you when you visit or shop at Zidoff.com, use Zidoff products or services, use Zidoff applications for mobile, or use software provided by Zidoff in connection with any of the foregoing (collectively, "Zidoff Services"). Zidoff provides the Zidoff Services subject to the following conditions.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h4>By using Zidoff Services, you agree to these conditions. Please read them carefully.</h4>\r\n<p>We offer a wide range of Zidoff Services, and sometimes additional terms may apply. When you use a Zidoff Service (for example, Your Profile, or Zidoff applications for mobile) you will also be subjected to the guidelines, terms and agreements applicable to that Zidoff Service ("Service Terms"). If these Conditions of Use are inconsistent with the Service Terms, those Service Terms will take control.</p>\r\n<p>Any temporary business surcharges (i.e. security, airport, remote location or customs duties surcharges) not anticipated or converted at the time of quoting the final cost of an order would be imposed on the buyer, who will be responsible for paying these charges prior to delivery.</p>', 1, 0, 1, '', '', 0, '35991362173', 1412805981, '::1', '1'),
('5579908658', 'terms_of_service', 'Privacy Standards', '<h4>Privacy Standards</h4>\r\n<p>Please review our Privacy Notice, which also governs your use of Zidoff Services, to understand our practices.</p>', 2, 0, 2, '1300130013', '35991362173', 1412793787, '35991362173', 1412793787, '::1', '1'),
('5579919836', 'terms_of_service', 'Electronic Communications', '<h4>Electronic Communications</h4>\r\n<p>When you use any of Zidoff Services, or send e-mails to us, you are communicating with us electronically. You consent to receive communications from us electronically. We will communicate with you by e-mail or by posting notices on this site or through the other Zidoff Services. You agree that all agreements, notices, disclosures and other communications that we provide to you electronically satisfy any legal requirement that such communications be in writing.</p>', 3, 0, 3, '1300130013', '35991362173', 1412793899, '35991362173', 1412793899, '::1', '1'),
('5579924126', 'terms_of_service', 'Copyright', '<h4>Copyright</h4>\r\n<p>All content included in or made available through any Zidoff Service, such as text, graphics, logos, button icons, images, audio clips, digital downloads, and data compilations is the property of Zidoff or its content suppliers and protected by Nigeria and International copyright laws. The compilation of all content included in or made available through any Zidoff Service is the exclusive property of Zidoff and protected by Nigeria and International copyright laws.</p>', 3, 0, 4, '1300130013', '35991362173', 1412793942, '35991362173', 1412793942, '::1', '1'),
('5579930615', 'terms_of_service', 'Trademarks', '<h4>Trademarks</h4>\r\n<p>In addition, graphics, logos, page headers, button icons, scripts, and service names included in or made available through any Zidoff Service are trademarks or trade dress of Zidoff in Nigeria and other countries. Zidoff''s trademarks and trade dress may not be used in connection with any product or service that is not Zidoff''s, in any manner that is likely to cause confusion among customers or in any manner that disparages or discredits Zidoff. All other trademarks not owned by Zidoff that appear in any Zidoff Service are the property of their respective owners, who may or may not be affiliated with, connected to, or sponsored by Zidoff.</p>', 5, 0, 5, '1300130013', '35991362173', 1412794007, '35991362173', 1412794007, '::1', '1'),
('5579935712', 'terms_of_service', 'License and Access', '<h4>License and Access</h4>\r\n<p>Subject to your compliance with these Conditions of Use and your payment of any applicable fees, Zidoff or its content providers grant you a limited, non-exclusive, non-transferable, non-sublicensable license to access and make personal and non-commercial use of the Zidoff Services. This license does not include any re-sale or commercial use of any Zidoff Service, or its contents; any collection and use of any product listings, descriptions, or prices; any derivative use of any Zidoff Service or its contents; any downloading or copying of account information for the benefit of another merchant; or any use of data mining, robots, or similar data gathering and extraction tools. All rights not expressly granted to you in these Conditions of Use or any Service Terms are reserved and retained by Zidoff or its licensors, suppliers, publishers, rights-holders, or other content providers. No Zidoff Service, nor any part of any Zidoff Service, may be reproduced, duplicated, copied, sold, resold, visited, or otherwise exploited for any commercial purpose without express written consent of Zidoff. You may not frame or utilize framing techniques to enclose any trademark, logo, or other proprietary information (including images, text, page layout, or form) of Zidoff without express written consent. You may not use any meta tags or any other "hidden text" utilizing Zidoff''s name or trademarks without the express written consent of Zidoff. You may not misuse the Zidoff Services. You may use the Zidoff Services only as permitted by law. The licenses granted by Zidoff terminates if you do not comply with these Conditions of Use or any Service Terms.</p>', 6, 0, 6, '1300130013', '35991362173', 1412794058, '35991362173', 1412794058, '::1', '1'),
('5579969549', 'terms_of_service', 'Your Account', '<h4>Your Account</h4>\r\n<p>If you use any Zidoff Service, you are responsible for maintaining the confidentiality of your account and password, for restricting access to your computer, and you agree to accept responsibility for all activities that occur under your account or password. Zidoff sells products for children, but it sells them to adults, who can purchase with a credit card or other permitted payment method. If you are under 18, Zidoff reserves the right to contract with children of under 18 with respect to contracts of necessities under the established principles of law of contract. You may use the Zidoff Services only with involvement of a parent or guardian. Alcohol listings on Zidoff are intended for adults. You must be at least 21 years of age to purchase alcohol, or use any site functionality related to alcohol. Zidoff reserves the right to refuse service, terminate accounts, remove or edit content, or cancel orders in its sole discretion.</p>', 7, 0, 7, '1300130013', '35991362173', 1412794396, '35991362173', 1412794396, '::1', '1'),
('5579977812', 'terms_of_service', 'Reviews, Comments, Communications, and Other Content', '<h4>Reviews, Comments, Communications, and Other Content</h4>\r\n<p>Visitors may post reviews, comments, photos, and other content; send e-cards and other communications; and submit suggestions, ideas, comments, questions, or other information, so long as the content is not illegal, obscene, threatening, defamatory, invasive of privacy, infringing of intellectual property rights, or otherwise injurious to third parties or objectionable and does not consist of or contain software viruses, political campaigning, commercial solicitation, chain letters, mass mailings, or any form of "spam." You may not use a false e-mail address, impersonate any person or entity, or otherwise mislead as to the origin of a card or other content. Zidoff reserves the right (but not the obligation) to remove or edit such content, but does not regularly review posted content.</p>\r\n<p>If you do post content or submit material, and unless we indicate otherwise, you grant Zidoff a non-exclusive, royalty-free, perpetual, irrevocable, and fully sublicensable right to use, reproduce, modify, adapt, publish, translate, create derivative works from, distribute, and display such content throughout the world in any media. You grant Zidoff and sublicense the right to use the name that you submit in connection with such content, if they choose. You represent and warrant that you own or otherwise control all of the rights to the content that you post; that the content is accurate; that use of the content you supply does not violate this policy and will not cause injury to any person or entity; and that you will indemnify Zidoff for all claims resulting from content you supply. Zidoff has the right but not the obligation to monitor and edit or remove any activity or content. Zidoff takes no responsibility and assumes no liability for any content posted by you or any third party.</p>\r\n<p>You have no right whatsoever to post any information that may reveal your direct contact details to the general public, or information that may render any of our services irrelevant without written permission from Zidoff.</p>', 8, 0, 8, '1300130013', '35991362173', 1412794479, '35991362173', 1412794479, '::1', '1'),
('5579981631', 'terms_of_service', 'Copyright Complaints', '<h4>Copyright Complaints</h4>\r\n<p>Zidoff respects the intellectual property of others. If you believe that your work has been copied in a way that constitutes copyright infringement, please follow our Notice and Procedure for Making Claims of Copyright Infringement.</p>', 9, 0, 9, '', '', 0, '35991362173', 1412794585, '::1', '1'),
('5579985050', 'terms_of_service', 'Risk of Loss', '<h4>Risk of Loss</h4>\r\n<p>All items purchased from Zidoff are made pursuant to a shipment contract. This means that the risk of loss and title for such items pass to you upon our delivery to the carrier.</p>', 10, 0, 10, '1300130013', '35991362173', 1412794551, '35991362173', 1412794551, '::1', '1'),
('5579993226', 'terms_of_service', 'Returns, Refunds and Title', '<h4>Returns, Refunds and Title</h4>\r\n<p>Zidoff does not take title to returned items until the item arrives at any of our offices. At our discretion, a refund may be issued without requiring a return. In this situation, Zidoff does not take title to the refunded item. For more information about our returns and refunds, please see our Return Policy.</p>', 11, 0, 11, '1300130013', '35991362173', 1412794633, '35991362173', 1412794633, '::1', '1'),
('5579996952', 'terms_of_service', 'Product Description', '<h4>Product Description</h4>\r\n<p>Zidoff attempts to be as accurate as possible. However, Zidoff does not warrant that product descriptions or other content of any Zidoff Service is accurate, complete, reliable, current, or error-free. If a product offered by Zidoff itself is not as described, your sole remedy is to return it in unused condition.</p>\r\n<p>However on occasions where a seller has mislead a buyer with inaccurate and/or incomplete description of their products, and the buyer receives and returns the items to Zidoff, Zidoff will confiscate the items and refund the buyer.</p>\r\n<p>When listing used products, sellers should capture the exact image of the item to be sold, and explicitly describe the current state or specific fault of the item if any, failure to do so will also result in confistication of the item, which may be returned back to the seller if he/she decides to pay for the additional charges incurred by Zidoff.</p>', 12, 0, 12, '1300130013', '35991362173', 1412794670, '35991362173', 1412794670, '::1', '1'),
('5580001477', 'terms_of_service', 'Pricing', '<h4>Pricing</h4>\r\n<p>Except where noted otherwise, the List Price or Suggested Price displayed for products on any Zidoff Service represents the full retail price listed on the product itself, suggested by the merchant. The List Price or Suggested Price is a comparative price estimate and may or may not represent the prevailing price in every area on any particular day. Where an item is offered for sale by one of our merchants, the List Price or Suggested Price may be provided by the merchant.</p>\r\n<p class="Default">Â </p>\r\n<p>Orders that are shipped to countries outside the Merchant Country may be subject to import taxes, customs tariffs, and fees levied by the destination country or the shipping company. These charges are the customer''s responsibility and will be billed by the delivery company. We have no control over these charges and are unable to estimate them. Tariffs and taxes are neither collected nor included in your price calculation at the time of your order; for an estimate of these fees, which vary by region, contact the customs office in your area.</p>\r\n<p>Purchases are shipped with the terms CIF or DDU, thus indicating that the buyer is responsible for paying all tariffs and taxes when the goods arrive. The delivery service will either take the package to the buyer''s address and release it only after the buyer has paid all applicable tariffs and taxes, or will send a note informing him/her that his package has arrived, that tariffs and taxes are owed, and that the package will be released only upon payment of those charges.</p>\r\n<p>With respect to items sold on Zidoff, we cannot confirm the price of an item until it gets delivered to you. Despite our best efforts, a small number of the items in our catalog may incur additional charges due to shipping and handling such as custom duties, remote location, pick up, overweight piece, oversized piece, and dangerous goods. In cases like this, you will be notified to pay the additional charge within a period of 5 working days before items will be delivered to you, failure to do so will result in cancellation of the order without any refund.</p>', 13, 0, 13, '', '', 0, '35991362173', 1412794750, '::1', '1'),
('5580012128', 'terms_of_service', 'Escrow Agreement', '<h4>Escrow Agreement</h4>\r\n<p>In an attempt to build trust in our customers'' Zidoff.com provides an Escrow Service that is aimed at protecting buyers. Zidoff.com holds a trust account in her name that would assure payment to a seller for goods sold or reimbursement of funds to a buyer for goods purchased on her ecommerce portal. When you list an item(s) for sale on the Zidoff.com website you agree to the following terms:</p>\r\n<p>To ensure that the item is physically available and will continue to remain ready for delivery during the life of the listing and if at any point in time the items is no longer available, to immediately update the quantity of the item listed, or contact the Zidoff.com customer service. Failure to do such will result in merchants being penalized a fee or may even lead to the complete closure of the merchants account.</p>\r\n<p>By listing items for sale on the Zidoff.com website, you also agree to automatically allow Zidoff.com, any of its agents, or partner companies to pick-up the items listed from your location without providing any form of financial compensation until the product has been delivered to, and inspected by the buyer to confirm that such an item(s) matches the specifications stated by you the merchant. Please refer to our Return Policy for detailed explanation on the cases that may lead to product return.</p>\r\n<p>You also agree to package and make products ordered ready for pick-up by Zidoff.com. With respect to this you will ensure the packaging of the items are carried out in the way and manner as instructed to you by the email that you will receive from Zidoff.com</p>', 14, 0, 14, '1300130013', '35991362173', 1412794822, '35991362173', 1412794822, '::1', '1'),
('5580021925', 'terms_of_service', 'Payment', '<h4>Payment</h4>\r\n<p>Zidoff provides a very easy, secured and effective payment system, buyers and sellers can pay from the comfort of their homes via e-payments option: Visa card, master card and e-Transact or wire transfer to our account, we keep track of every payment and orders, the buyer is constantly updated with this information.</p>\r\n<p>However you might experience some delays during payment due to the following</p>\r\n\r\nYour own internet speed\r\nThe transfer switch mishap\r\n\r\n<p>Zidoff advices sellers to confirm from their local bank the cost of transaction (this is the fee that the seller''s bank charges the seller when paid for items sold through Zidoff.com) and include that on the selling price of their items.</p>\r\n<p>All payments required to be made by the user through the payment gateway shall be payable unconditionally, without any deduction, claim, counterclaim, set-off, notice or demand.</p>\r\n<p>Zidoff may revise the fees or charges from time to time and shall notify the Merchant of any such changes in writing.</p>\r\n<p>If a transaction involving payment by Users under the Systems is rejected for any reason whatsoever, the user should agree to alternative means of payment with Zidoff</p>\r\n<p>The user agrees that where multiple or excess payments have been effected by or on behalf of Users in respect of any transaction using the Services, zidoff shall refund or reimburse such Users for such excess payments made</p>\r\n<p>The user further agrees that no liability shall be imputed to Zidoff, where it is confirmed that zidoff relied on a cost quote/price list furnished by the user in relaying information for a transaction to a buyer and such cost quote is later discovered to be materially incorrect.</p>\r\n<p>Any fraud, dishonesty or misconduct (criminal or otherwise) relating to the transactions perpetrated by the user, its servants, agents, employees or contractors or the fraud, dishonesty or misconduct (criminal or otherwise) perpetrated by a third party as a result of the negligence or default of the user, its servants, agents, employees or contractors.</p>\r\n<p>Any loss arising from any fraud or dishonesty arising from a breach of security of the Merchant''s details, software or hardware by a third party.</p>', 15, 0, 15, '1300130013', '35991362173', 1412794920, '35991362173', 1412794920, '::1', '1'),
('5580030262', 'terms_of_service', 'Delivery', '<h4>Delivery</h4>\r\n<p>It is the buyer''s responsibility to ensure that the product can be lawfully imported to the destination country. The recipient must bear any additional charges for customs clearance; we have no control over such charges and cannot predict what they may be.</p>\r\n<p>We employ the services of timely experts such as DHL to handle all deliveries, so be very assured your items will get to you just in time. But for deliveries spanning over a country''s borders, custom delays may hinder the items being delivered at the exact stated time</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>DHL TERMS AND CONDITIONS</p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>The DHL Express Terms and Conditions of carriage as described overleaf on each DHL waybill shall apply to all consignments that we export or import using DHL services without exception.</li>\r\n<li>The agreed rates are exclusive of government taxes and other surcharges, and are valid only until December 31 of the year the rates are quoted. The rates are subject to a General Price Increase effective 1st&nbsp;January of each year.</li>\r\n<li>The agreed rates are valid so long as shipments to the value of a minimum of N50,000 (Fifty thousand Naira only) are exported or imported by DHL International Nigeria Limited (Express), otherwise the agreement will be renegotiated.</li>\r\n<li>The agreed rates are based on the shipment volumes and profiles that have been provided by the Customer. In the event of a shortfall on the projected volumes or a substantial change in the weight or destination mix, DHL reserves the right to revise the rates at any time upon prior written notice to the Customer.</li>\r\n<li>DHL reserves the right to revise the rates at any time upon prior written notice to the Customer if there is a substantial change in the Customer''s service requirements, the local currency''s exchange rate to EUR/USD or in DHL''s costs.</li>\r\n<li>We also recognise that all shipments are reweighed by DHL and that charges will be based on this final weight.</li>\r\n<li>For large, lightweight shipments DHL International Nigeria Ltd (Express) complies with IATA regulations and charges the greater of either the volumetric weight or the actual weight. The volumetric weight is calculated by multiplying the width by the length by the depth of the shipment and the total divided by 5,000 e.g. for a consignment with the dimensions 50cm by 40cm by 30cm, volumetric weight will be equal to (50x40x30)/5000 = 12kg (Subject to change with IATA resolution 502)</li>\r\n<li>All DHL International Nigeria Ltd (Express) invoices (inbound and outbound) are to be paid strictly within 30 days from the date of invoice. Invoices on Duty Accounts are to be paid within 7 days of invoice date.</li>\r\n<li>DHL reserves the right to withdraw the credit facility if two invoices are unsettled on two consecutive months unless special arrangements are made and confirmed in writing by DHL International Nigeria Ltd (Express)</li>\r\n<li>Unless agreed in writing, all DHL invoices will be delivered on a weekly basis to the invoice contact person designated by our organisation.</li>\r\n<li>DHL reserves the right to announce/impose temporary business surcharges (i.e. fuel, security, airport, customs surcharges) not converted or anticipated at the time of quoting DHL''s normal inclusive tariff.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p>No waiver or amendment of this agreement shall be binding on DHL International Nigeria Ltd (Express) or ourselves unless in writing and signed by a duly authorised representative of DHL International Nigeria Ltd (Express) and the duly authorised representative of our organisation/company</p>', 16, 0, 16, '', '', 0, '35991362173', 1412795627, '::1', '1'),
('5580034739', 'terms_of_service', 'Auctioning', '<h4>Auctioning</h4>\r\n<p>The Zidoff platform provides sellers the ability to auction items for a specific period of time for a fee; buyers can bid for the listed items within that period of time allocated for the auction. When an auction period has expired the seller will need to relist the remaining items for normal sale as the auction listing duration overrides the initial listing.</p>\r\n<p>Buyers should be aware that winning a bid doesn''t mean the item(s) would be sold to them, as it''s the decision of the seller to choose who to sell the item(s) to or choose not to sell the item(s) at all, likewise a buyer who has won a bid can decide not pay for the item.</p>', 17, 0, 17, '1300130013', '35991362173', 1412795048, '35991362173', 1412795048, '::1', '1'),
('5580038473', 'terms_of_service', 'Zidoff Software Terms', '<h4>Zidoff Software Terms</h4>\r\n<p>In addition to these Conditions of Use, the terms found here apply to any software (including any updates or upgrades to the software and any related documentation) that we make available to you from time to time for your use in connection with Zidoff Services.</p>', 18, 0, 18, '1300130013', '35991362173', 1412795085, '35991362173', 1412795085, '::1', '1'),
('5580042768', 'terms_of_service', 'Disclaimer of Warranties and Limitation of Liability', '<h4>Disclaimer of Warranties and Limitation of Liability</h4>\r\n<p>THE ZIDOFF SERVICES AND ALL INFORMATION, CONTENT, MATERIALS, PRODUCTS (INCLUDING SOFTWARE) AND OTHER SERVICES INCLUDED ON OR OTHERWISE MADE AVAILABLE TO YOU THROUGH THE ZIDOFF SERVICES ARE PROVIDED BY ZIDOFF ON AN "AS IS" AND "AS AVAILABLE" BASIS, UNLESS OTHERWISE SPECIFIED IN WRITING. ZIDOFF MAKES NO REPRESENTATIONS OR WARRANTIES OF ANY KIND, EXPRESS OR IMPLIED, AS TO THE OPERATION OF THE ZIDOFF SERVICES, OR THE INFORMATION, CONTENT, MATERIALS, PRODUCTS (INCLUDING SOFTWARE) OR OTHER SERVICES INCLUDED ON OR OTHERWISE MADE AVAILABLE TO YOU THROUGH THE ZIDOFF SERVICES, UNLESS OTHERWISE SPECIFIED IN WRITING. YOU EXPRESSLY AGREE THAT YOUR USE OF THE ZIDOFF SERVICES IS AT YOUR SOLE RISK.</p>\r\n<p>TO THE FULL EXTENT PERMISSIBLE BY APPLICABLE LAW, ZIDOFF DISCLAIMS ALL WARRANTIES, EXPRESS OR IMPLIED, INCLUDING, BUT NOT LIMITED TO, IMPLIED WARRANTIES OF MERCHANTABILITY AND FITNESS FOR A PARTICULAR PURPOSE. ZIDOFF DOES NOT WARRANT THAT THE ZIDOFF SERVICES, INFORMATION, CONTENT, MATERIALS, PRODUCTS (INCLUDING SOFTWARE) OR OTHER SERVICES INCLUDED ON OR OTHERWISE MADE AVAILABLE TO YOU THROUGH THE ZIDOFF SERVICES, ZIDOFF''S SERVERS OR ELECTRONIC COMMUNICATIONS SENT FROM ZIDOFF ARE FREE OF VIRUSES OR OTHER HARMFUL COMPONENTS. ZIDOFF WILL NOT BE LIABLE FOR ANY DAMAGES OF ANY KIND ARISING FROM THE USE OF ANY ZIDOFF SERVICE, OR FROM ANY INFORMATION, CONTENT, MATERIALS, PRODUCTS (INCLUDING SOFTWARE) OR OTHER SERVICES INCLUDED ON OR OTHERWISE MADE AVAILABLE TO YOU THROUGH ANY ZIDOFF SERVICE, INCLUDING, BUT NOT LIMITED TO DIRECT, INDIRECT, INCIDENTAL, PUNITIVE, AND CONSEQUENTIAL DAMAGES, UNLESS OTHERWISE SPECIFIED IN WRITING.</p>\r\n<p>CERTAIN STATE LAWS DO NOT ALLOW LIMITATIONS ON IMPLIED WARRANTIES OR THE EXCLUSION OR LIMITATION OF CERTAIN DAMAGES. IF THESE LAWS APPLY TO YOU, SOME OR ALL OF THE ABOVE DISCLAIMERS, EXCLUSIONS, OR LIMITATIONS MAY NOT APPLY TO YOU, AND YOU MIGHT HAVE ADDITIONAL RIGHTS.</p>', 19, 0, 19, '1300130013', '35991362173', 1412795128, '35991362173', 1412795128, '::1', '1'),
('5580047545', 'terms_of_service', 'Site Policies, Modification, and Severability', '<h4>Site Policies, Modification, and Severability</h4>\r\n<p>Please review our other policies, such as our privacy policy and return policy posted on this site. These policies also govern your use of Zidoff Services. We reserve the right to make changes to our site, policies and service terms at any time. If any of these conditions shall be deemed invalid, void, or for any reason unenforceable, that condition shall be deemed severable and shall not affect the validity and enforceability of any remaining condition.</p>', 20, 0, 20, '1300130013', '35991362173', 1412795176, '35991362173', 1412795176, '::1', '1'),
('5580052759', 'terms_of_service', 'Notice and Procedure for Making Claims of Copyright Infringement', '<h4>Notice and Procedure for Making Claims of Copyright Infringement</h4>\r\n<p>If you believe that your work has been copied in a way that constitutes copyright infringement, please submit your complaint using our online form. We respond quickly to the concerns of rights owners about any alleged infringement.</p>\r\n<p>If you prefer to submit a report in writing, please provide us with this information:</p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>A physical signature of the person authorized to act on behalf of the owner of the copyright interest;</li>\r\n<li>A description of the copyrighted work that you claim has been infringed upon;</li>\r\n<li>A description of where the material that you claim is infringing is located on the site;</li>\r\n<li>Your address, telephone number, and e-mail address;</li>\r\n<li>A statement by you that you have a good-faith belief that the disputed use is not authorized by the copyright owner, its agent, or the law;</li>\r\n<li>A statement by you, made under penalty of perjury, that the above information in your notice is accurate and that you are the copyright owner or authorized to act on the copyright owner''s behalf.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p>Zidoff''s Copyright Agent for notice of claims of copyright infringement on its site can be reached as follows:</p>\r\n<p>Copyright Agent</p>\r\n<p>Zidoff Online Commerce Limited,</p>\r\n<p>Suit B24 Fanaha (TJ 1407) Business Plaza</p>\r\n<p>Behind AP Plaza, off Adetokunbo Ademola Crescent,</p>\r\n<p>Wuse 2 Abuja</p>\r\n<p>08080744191</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>Please note that this procedure is exclusively for notifying Zidoff that your copyrighted material has been infringed.</p>', 21, 0, 21, '', '', 0, '35991362173', 1412795898, '::1', '1'),
('5580058317', 'terms_of_service', 'Additional Zidoff Software Terms', '<h4>Additional Zidoff Software Terms</h4>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Use of the Zidoff Software.&nbsp;You may use Zidoff Software solely for purposes of enabling you to use and enjoy the Zidoff Services as provided by Zidoff, and as permitted by the Conditions of Use, these Software Terms and any Service Terms. You may not incorporate any portion of the Zidoff Software into your own programs or compile any portion of it in combination with your own programs, transfer it for use with another service, or sell, rent, lease, lend, loan, distribute or sub-license the Zidoff Software or otherwise assign any rights to the Zidoff Software in whole or in part. You may not use the Zidoff Software for any illegal purpose. We may cease providing any Zidoff Software and we may terminate your right to use any Zidoff Software at any time. Your rights to use the Zidoff Software will automatically terminate without notice from us if you fail to comply with any of these Software Terms of Service, the Conditions of Use or any other Service Terms. Additional third party terms contained within or distributed with certain Zidoff Software that are specifically identified in related documentation may apply to that Zidoff Software (or software incorporated with the Zidoff Software) and will govern the use of such software in the event of a conflict with these Conditions of Use. All software used in any Zidoff Service is the property of Zidoff or its software suppliers and protected by Nigeria and international copyright laws.</li>\r\n<li>Use of Third Party Services.&nbsp;When you use the Zidoff Software, you may also be using the services of one or more third parties, such as a wireless carrier or a mobile platform provider. Your use of these third party services may be subject to the separate policies, terms of use, and fees of these third parties.</li>\r\n<li>No Reverse Engineering.&nbsp;You may not, and you will not encourage, assist or authorize any other person to copy, modify, reverse engineer, decompile or disassemble, or otherwise tamper with, the Zidoff Software, whether in whole or in part, or create any derivative works from or of the Zidoff Software.</li>\r\n<li>Updates.&nbsp;In order to keep the Zidoff Software up-to-date, we may offer automatic or manual updates at any time and without notice to you.</li>\r\n<li>Export Regulations; Government End Users.&nbsp;You must comply with all export and re-export restrictions and regulations of the Ministry of Trade and Commerce and other Nigerian agencies and authorities that may apply to the Zidoff Software.</li>\r\n</ul>', 22, 0, 22, '', '', 0, '35991362173', 1412795548, '::1', '1'),
('5581152352', 'return_policy', 'Introduction', '<p><span style="font-family: ''courier new'', courier;">Last modified: October 14, 2013</span></p>\r\n<h4>Overview</h4>\r\n<p>The services provided here at Zidoff.com are all dependent on our terms and conditions, thus we advise you to take your time to properly read and understand all these terms before using the services. We very much believe that if you go on and shop through Zidoff.com that you agree to these conditions.</p>', 1, 0, 23, '1300130013', '35991362173', 1412806224, '35991362173', 1412806224, '::1', '1'),
('5581182244', 'return_policy', 'Zidoff Return Policy', '<h4>Zidoff Return Policy</h4>\r\n<p>Return policy governs our agreement with you the buyer regarding refunds on all items bought on Zidoff.com, and it''s valid in situations where the received item(s) does not meet the specification provided by the seller, only then do the buyer have the right to request a refund of his/her payment. This procedure is totally handled by Zidoff and NOT the seller and we advise that it be done immediately as buyers are given only 24 hours to assess the item(s) delivered and request for refund if not satisfied. Please note that you won''t be able to request a refund after 24hours of receiving and assessing the item(s).</p>\r\n<p>Sellers should know that Zidoff.com highly appreciates their commitment to the platform and has put a strict return policy so it''s only on situations where the item(s) received by the user does not meet the specification provided by the seller that the buyer can request a refund of his/her payment, this procedure is totally handled by Zidoff NOT you the seller, we have also established a return request period of only 24 hours to further consolidate your trust on our platform</p>\r\n<p>Zidoff.com also do a regular investigation on every refund request case to make sure the stance are aligned to the return policy and the returned item(s) reach the seller in good condition if that is the case. Zidoff.com uses Escrow services to protect the buyer from fraud and encourage our services users; as such sellers will not get the money paid by buyer until after 24 hours of delivery.</p>', 2, 0, 24, '1300130013', '35991362173', 1412806523, '35991362173', 1412806523, '::1', '1'),
('5581188433', 'return_policy', 'Conditions for Item Return / Payment Refund', '<h4>Conditions for Item Return / Payment Refund</h4>\r\n<p>Below is a list of situations that might guarantee a refund of payments to the buyer.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><strong>Bad Product Quality</strong></p>\r\n<p>This refers to cases where the product is non-functional, partly-functional or simply does not live up to expectations, and such condition was not explicitly stated by the seller while describing the product.</p>\r\n<p>Non-functional product examples:</p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Mobile phones not working because of different transmission frequency</li>\r\n<li>Songs cannot be stored into MP3 players</li>\r\n<li>DVD players not in customized language as required</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p>Partly-functional product examples:</p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Faulty USB cables for MP3 players</li>\r\n<li>Broken clock hands</li>\r\n<li>Mobile Phones with extremely short battery life</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p>In cases like the above, the responsibility falls on the supplier.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><strong>Counterfeit Goods</strong></p>\r\n<p>This refers to cases where the item(s) delivered was labelled with an unauthorized brand name or logo.</p>\r\n<p>In cases of disparity:</p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Both buyer and supplier will be held responsible if both parties knowingly trade in counterfeit goods</li>\r\n<li>The buyer will be held responsible if the supplier provides valid and authorized evidence proving the authenticity of their products</li>\r\n<li>The supplier will be held responsible if they fail to provide valid and authorized evidence proving the authenticity of their products or if guilt is admitted</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><strong>Quantity Not As Described</strong></p>\r\n<p>This refers to cases where the buyer receives the items less than originally ordered in numbers.</p>\r\n<p>Examples of items received less than originally ordered:</p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Goods lacking in necessary parts</li>\r\n<li>Shortage of goods from the supplier</li>\r\n<li>The supplier ships the goods in batches</li>\r\n<li>The quantity description by the supplier is not accurate</li>\r\n<li>Empty package(s) received</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p>In cases like this, the supplier will be held responsible if the buyer manages to provide valid evidence such as receipt of delivery, photos, etc.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><strong>Products Not As Described</strong></p>\r\n<p>This refers to cases where the Item(s) received are not as what was agreed upon.</p>\r\n<p>Examples:</p>\r\n<p>Supplier shipped the wrong item</p>\r\n<p>In cases this case the supplier will be held responsible if the buyer manages to provide valid evidence such as receipt of delivery, photos, etc.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><strong>The received goods are damaged</strong></p>\r\n<p>In cases of dispute, the buyer will be held responsible if he/she accepts delivery even though the outer packaging is damaged. For damages to the products, the supplier will be held responsible provided that valid evidence such as photos and/or videos are available.</p>', 3, 0, 25, '', '', 0, '35991362173', 1412806662, '::1', '1'),
('5581204574', 'return_policy', 'Item Return / Payment Refund Process', '<h4>Item Return / Payment Refund Process</h4>\r\n<p>The payment refund process needs to be done discretely with Zidoff, as the buyer doesn''t have direct access to the seller to complain. The process of asking for refunds is a task on its own and proper procedures must be followed before a buyer''s request is processed within the subsequent paragraphs we''ll discuss in detail the process and even the implications.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><strong>1 Before purchase</strong></p>\r\n<p>In as much as Zidoff.com has a strong product listing and detailing policy for seller to honestly present products that match their description we also strongly advice that before purchase of any item(s) off Zidoff, buyers should review the items very well before making a purchase.</p>\r\n<p>It''s also very important for buyer''s to known that Returns cannot be based on time of delivery of items(delayed delivery) ordered this is because of the huge uncertainty possible in the system, the varying delivery conditions from the country/region of purchase to the seller''s region/country, Zidoff.com will however process buyer''s orders as soon as a payment has been made, and item(s) will be collected as soon as possible from the sellers destination, and tracking number will be issued by the courier agency for the buyer to follow up their items.</p>\r\n<p><strong>2 Implications</strong></p>\r\n<p>The refund of payments will pass through a process similar to the process made during payment, similarly the return and handling of the items would also follow a reverse process to that made during the initial delivery of the item. Should a buyer''s request for refund go through successfully, the costs of delivery of the item(s) back to seller, bank charges and commissions would be deducted from the amount that will be repaid to the buyer.</p>\r\n<p><strong>3 Estimated return amount</strong></p>\r\n<p>When a refund has successfully been processed, the buyer will not get the total amount they paid for the item(s) delivered, the overhead of delivery cost and transaction charge will be the responsibility of the buyer but in a situation where we investigate the matter and find that the seller has forwarded an item(s) that don''t match in anyway the product listed on Zidoff.com or any of the other conditions listed above, we will consider that as fraud and will confiscate the items and blacklist the seller from further use of Zidoff.com services.</p>\r\n<p><strong>4 Estimated return Period</strong></p>\r\n<p>Transaction periods often take a day or more for wire transfer, Zidoff.com will do all it can to return the payments made by a buyer as soon as the seller confirms receipt of the returned item, and is satisfied with the item''s condition. Because refunds go through the normal transfer rerouting before it gets to the buyer, an interval of 2-4 working days might just be sufficient before refund is received</p>\r\n<p>The process:</p>\r\n<p>Bank wire transfers are often the most expedient method for transferring funds between bank accounts. A bank wire transfer is affected as follows:</p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>The entity wishing to do a transfer approaches a bank and gives the bank the order to transfer a certain amount of money. IBAN and BIC codes are given as well so the bank knows where the money needs to be sent.</li>\r\n<li>The sending bank transmits a message, via a secure system (such as SWIFT or Fedwire), to the receiving bank, requesting that it effect payment according to the instructions given.</li>\r\n<li>The message also includes settlement instructions. The actual transfer is not instantaneous: funds may take several hours or even days to move from the sender''s account to the receiver''s account.</li>\r\n<li>Either the banks</li>\r\n</ul>', 4, 0, 26, '1300130013', '35991362173', 1412806746, '35991362173', 1412806746, '::1', '1'),
('5581211458', 'return_policy', 'The Return Procedure', '<h4>The Return Procedure</h4>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Buyer receives the item(s) ordered</li>\r\n<li>Reviews the item(s) within the first 24hours</li>\r\n<li>Visits the Zidoff website</li>\r\n<li>Opens a Support Ticket</li>\r\n<li>Input the order number of that particular item(s)</li>\r\n<li>Zidoff processes the request and emails the buyer a return ticket number</li>\r\n<li>Which he/she prints and attached</li>\r\n<li>Prepare the package as it was on the time of delivery</li>\r\n<li>Attach the return ticket on the package</li>\r\n<li>Our courier partner will come and pick it up from your address, or you may have to take the item to any of our courier partner''s office depending on your location and choice of courier partner.</li>\r\n<li>As the package enters the delivery system, the seller receives a tracking number</li>\r\n<li>Seller receives the package and notifies Zidoff.com</li>\r\n</ul>', 5, 0, 27, '1300130013', '35991362173', 1412806815, '35991362173', 1412806815, '::1', '1'),
('5581230572', 'privacy_policy', 'Introduction', '<p><span style="font-family: ''courier new'', courier;">Last modified: October 14, 2013</span></p>\r\n<div class="heading">\r\n<h4>Privacy Policy</h4>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="content">\r\n<p>This Privacy Policy describes how we handle your personal information for our services on the Zidoff websites. It applies generally to the Zidoff.com website and content where this policy appears in the footer of the page. The policy that applies on any of our domains or sub domains is always the policy that appears in the footer of each website.</p>\r\n<p>We strive to provide a consistent set of privacy practices throughout the global Zidoff trading community. By accepting the Privacy Policy and the User Agreement in registration, you expressly consent to our collection, storage, use and disclosure of your personal information as described in this Privacy Policy. This Privacy Policy is effective upon completion of the registration process for new users.</p>\r\n</div>', 1, 0, 28, '1300130013', '35991362173', 1412807006, '35991362173', 1412807006, '::1', '1'),
('5581235031', 'privacy_policy', 'Collection', '<h4>Collection</h4>\r\n<p>You can browse our sites without telling us who you are or revealing any personal information about yourself. Once you give us your personal information, you are not anonymous to us. If you choose to provide us with personal information, you consent to the transfer and storage of that information on our servers</p>\r\n<p>We may collect and store the following personal information:</p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>email address, physical contact information, and (depending on the service used) sometimes financial information, such as bank account numbers;</li>\r\n<li>transactional information based on your activities on the sites (such as bidding, buying, selling, item and content you generate or that relates to your account);</li>\r\n<li>shipping, billing and other information you provide to purchase or ship an item;</li>\r\n<li>community discussions, chats, dispute resolution, feedback, correspondence through our sites, and correspondence sent to us;</li>\r\n<li>other information from your interaction with our sites, services, content and advertising, including computer/device and connection information, statistics on page views, traffic to and from the sites, ad data, IP address and standard web log information;</li>\r\n<li>additional information we ask you to submit to authenticate yourself or if we believe you are violating site policies (for example, we may ask you to send us an ID or bill to verify your address, or to answer additional questions online to help verify your identity or ownership of an item you list);</li>\r\n<li>information from other companies, such as demographic and navigation data</li>\r\n</ul>', 2, 0, 29, '1300130013', '35991362173', 1412807051, '35991362173', 1412807051, '::1', '1'),
('5581238520', 'privacy_policy', 'Use', '<h4>Use</h4>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Our primary purpose in collecting personal information is to provide you with a safe, smooth, efficient, and customized experience. You agree that we may use your personal information to:</li>\r\n<li>provide the services and customer support you request;</li>\r\n<li>resolve disputes, collect fees, and make payments;</li>\r\n<li>prevent, detect, and investigate potentially prohibited or illegal activities, and enforce our User Agreement;</li>\r\n<li>customize, measure and improve our services, content and advertising;</li>\r\n<li>tell you about our services and those of our corporate family, targeted marketing, service updates, and promotional offers based on your communication preferences</li>\r\n<li>to send marketing communications via email (which you may chose not to receive at any time by changing your communications preferences in My Zidoff or following the instructions provided with the communication); and</li>\r\n<li>compare information for accuracy, and verify it with third parties</li>\r\n</ul>', 3, 0, 30, '1300130013', '35991362173', 1412807086, '35991362173', 1412807086, '::1', '1'),
('5581242424', 'privacy_policy', 'Marketing', '<h4>Marketing</h4>\r\n<p>We don''t sell or rent your personal information to third parties for their marketing purposes without your explicit consent. We may combine your information with information on other users and information we collect from other companies and use it to improve and personalize our services, content and advertising. If you don''t wish to receive marketing communications from us or participate in our adverts please inform us.</p>', 4, 0, 31, '1300130013', '35991362173', 1412807125, '35991362173', 1412807125, '::1', '1'),
('5581247054', 'privacy_policy', 'Our Disclosure of Your Information', '<h4>Our Disclosure of Your Information</h4>\r\n<p>We may disclose personal information to provide our service, respond to legal requirements, enforce our policies, respond to claims that a listing or other content infringes the rights of others, or protect anyone''s rights, property, or safety.</p>\r\n<p>We may also share your personal information with:</p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Service providers under contract who help with our business operations (such as fraud investigations, bill collection, delivery and customer support).</li>\r\n<li>Other third parties to whom you explicitly ask us to send your information (or about whom you are otherwise explicitly notified and consent to when using a specific service).</li>\r\n<li>Law enforcement agencies, other governmental agencies or third parties in response to a request for information relating to a criminal investigation, alleged illegal activity or any other activity that may expose us, you or any other Zidoff user to legal liability. The personal information we disclose may include your Email address and Email address history, name, city, state or province, telephone number, email address, fraud complaints and bidding and listing history or anything else that we deem relevant.</li>\r\n<li>Zidoff in connection with an investigation of fraud, intellectual property infringement, piracy, or other unlawful activity, as we in our sole discretion believe necessary or appropriate, either under confidentiality agreement or as required by law. In such circumstances, we may disclose name, street address, city, state or province, postcode, country, phone number, email address and company name.</li>\r\n<li>Other business entities, should we plan to merge with or be acquired by that business entity. (Should such a combination occur, we will require that the new combined entity follow this privacy policy with respect to your personal information. If your personal information will be used contrary to this policy, you will receive prior notice.)</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p>Without limiting the above, in an effort to respect your privacy and our ability to keep the community free from those who attempt to carry out fraudulent or illegal activities on the site, we will not otherwise disclose your personal information to law enforcement, other government officials, or other third parties without a legally valid request, except when we believe in good faith that the disclosure of information is necessary to prevent imminent physical harm or financial loss or to report suspected illegal activity</p>', 5, 0, 32, '', '', 0, '35991362173', 1412807771, '::1', '1'),
('5581253550', 'privacy_policy', 'Information You Share on Zidoff', '<h4>Information You Share on Zidoff</h4>\r\n<p>Your Email address is displayed throughout Zidoff (and so available to the public) and is connected to all of your Zidoff activity. Other people can see your bids, purchases, items for sale, shop fronts, feedback, ratings and associated comments. Notices sent to other community members about suspicious activity and policy breaches on our sites refer to Email address and specific items. So, if you associate your name with your Email address, the people to whom you have revealed your name will be able to personally identify your Zidoff activities. If you are a business seller, your contact details (such as name and geographical address) may be visible on the View Item page, as you indicate in your business preferences on My Zidoff.</p>\r\n<p>If you access our sites from a shared computer or a computer in an internet caf&eacute;, certain information about you, such as your Email address or reminders from Zidoff, may also be visible to other individuals who use the computer after you.</p>', 6, 0, 33, '1300130013', '35991362173', 1412807236, '35991362173', 1412807236, '::1', '1');
INSERT INTO `website_page_content` (`id`, `website_page_content001`, `website_page_content002`, `website_page_content003`, `website_page_content004`, `website_page_content005`, `serial_num`, `creator_role`, `created_by`, `creation_date`, `modified_by`, `modification_date`, `ip_address`, `record_status`) VALUES
('5581257573', 'privacy_policy', 'Using Information from Zidoff', '<h4>Using Information from Zidoff</h4>\r\n<p>Zidoff enables you to share personal and financial information to complete transactions. We encourage you to disclose your privacy practices and respect the privacy of other users. We cannot guarantee the privacy or security of your information and therefore we encourage you to evaluate the privacy and security policies of your trading partner before entering into a transaction and choosing to share your information. To help protect your privacy, we allow only limited access to other users'' contact and shipping information to facilitate your transactions. In all cases, you must comply with data protection laws, and give other users a chance to remove themselves from your database and a chance to review what information you have collected about them.</p>\r\n<p>You agree to use user information only for:</p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Zidoff transaction-related purposes that are not unsolicited commercial messages;</li>\r\n<li>using services offered through Zidoff (e.g. escrow, postage and fraud complaints), or</li>\r\n<li>other purposes that a user expressly chooses.</li>\r\n</ul>', 7, 0, 34, '', '', 0, '35991362173', 1412807706, '::1', '1'),
('5581261447', 'privacy_policy', 'Cookies', '<h4>Cookies</h4>\r\n<p>We use "cookies" (small files placed on your hard drive) on certain of our pages to help analyse our web page flow; customise our services, content and advertising; measure promotional effectiveness, and promote trust and safety.</p>\r\n<p>A few important things you should know about cookies are that:</p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>We offer certain features that are available only through the use of cookies.</li>\r\n<li>We use cookies to help identify you and maintain your signed-in status.</li>\r\n<li>Most cookies are "session cookies", meaning that they are automatically deleted from your hard drive at the end of a session.</li>\r\n<li>You are always free to decline our cookies if your browser permits, although doing so may interfere with your use of some of our sites or services.</li>\r\n<li>You may encounter cookies from third parties on certain pages of the sites that we do not control. (For example, if you view a web page created by another user, there may be a cookie placed by that web page.)</li>\r\n</ul>', 8, 0, 35, '1300130013', '35991362173', 1412807315, '35991362173', 1412807315, '::1', '1'),
('5581266965', 'privacy_policy', 'No Spam, Spyware or Spoofing', '<h4>No Spam, Spyware or Spoofing</h4>\r\n<p>We and our users do not tolerate spam. Make sure to set your Zidoff communication preferences so we communicate to you as you prefer. You are not licensed to add other Zidoff users, even a user who has purchased an item from you, to your mailing list (email or physical mail) without their express consent. To report Zidoff-related spam or spoof emails to Zidoff, please report it to us. You may not use our communication tools to send spam or otherwise send content that would breach our User Agreement. We automatically scan and may manually filter messages to check for spam, viruses, phishing attacks and other malicious activity or illegal or prohibited content, but we do not permanently store messages sent through these tools.</p>', 9, 0, 36, '1300130013', '35991362173', 1412807370, '35991362173', 1412807370, '::1', '1'),
('5581270869', 'privacy_policy', 'Account Protection', '<h4>Account Protection</h4>\r\n<p>Your password is the key to your account. Use unique numbers, letters and special characters, and do not disclose your Zidoff password to anyone. If you do share your password or your personal information with others, remember that you are responsible for all actions taken in the name of your account. If you lose control of your password, you may lose substantial control over your personal information and may be subject to legally binding actions taken on your behalf. Therefore, if your password has been compromised for any reason, you should immediately notify Zidoff and change your password.</p>', 10, 0, 37, '1300130013', '35991362173', 1412807409, '35991362173', 1412807409, '::1', '1'),
('5581279334', 'privacy_policy', 'Accessing and Changing Your Personal Information', '<h4>Accessing and Changing Your Personal Information</h4>\r\n<p>You can see, review and change most of your personal information by signing on to Zidoff. Generally, we will not manually modify your personal information because it is very difficult to verify your identity remotely. You must promptly update your personal information if it changes or is inaccurate. Upon your request to Customer Service, we will close your account and remove your personal information from view as soon as reasonably possible, based on your account activity and in accordance with applicable law. We do retain personal information from closed accounts to comply with law, prevent fraud, collect any fees owed, resolve disputes, troubleshoot problems, assist with any investigations, enforce our Zidoff User Agreement, and take other actions otherwise permitted by law.</p>', 11, 0, 38, '1300130013', '35991362173', 1412807494, '35991362173', 1412807494, '::1', '1'),
('5581283933', 'privacy_policy', 'Security', '<h4>Security</h4>\r\n<p>Your information is stored on our servers. We treat data as an asset that must be protected and use lots of tools (encryption, passwords, physical security, etc.) to protect your personal information against unauthorised access and disclosure. However, as you probably know, third parties may unlawfully intercept or access transmissions or private communications, and other users may abuse or misuse your personal information that they collect from the site. Therefore, although we work very hard to protect your privacy, we do not promise that your personal information or private communications will always remain private.</p>', 12, 0, 39, '1300130013', '35991362173', 1412807540, '35991362173', 1412807540, '::1', '1'),
('5581287159', 'privacy_policy', 'Third Parties', '<h4>Third Parties</h4>\r\n<p>Except as otherwise expressly included in this Privacy Policy, this document addresses only the use and disclosure of information we collect from you. If you disclose your information to others, whether they are bidders, buyers or sellers on our sites or other sites throughout the internet, different rules may apply to their use or disclosure of the information you disclose to them. Zidoff does not control the privacy policies of third parties, and you are subject to the privacy policies of those third parties where applicable. We encourage you to ask questions before you disclose your personal information to others.</p>', 13, 0, 40, '1300130013', '35991362173', 1412807572, '35991362173', 1412807572, '::1', '1'),
('5581290221', 'privacy_policy', 'Conclusion', '<h4>Conclusion</h4>\r\n<p>We may amend this Privacy Policy at any time by posting the amended terms on this site. All amended terms automatically take effect 30 days after they are initially posted. In addition, we will notify you through the Zidoff Message Centre or via email at the address you provide in My Zidoff account.</p>', 14, 0, 41, '1300130013', '35991362173', 1412807603, '35991362173', 1412807603, '::1', '1'),
('5581377547', 'about_us', 'Africa''s Gateway to Global Merchants', '<h3>Africa''s Gateway to Global Merchants</h3>\r\n<hr />\r\n<p>Zidoff.com is a global eCommerce platform, providing B2C (Business to Consumer) services toÂ it''s global customer base. Buyers can make purchases fromÂ a wide variety of products, ranging from Electronics, Fashion, Computers, Books and much more.Â TheseÂ products areÂ listed and marketed by various merchants worldwide, from over 150 countries.</p>\r\n<p>As an eCommerce company, we have provided buyers and sellers worldwide, a secure and reliable platform, for global trade. Our goal is to create a global marketplace without borders, provide more buying options to online shoppers and building their confidence in global trade. We also aim to expandÂ merchants outreach & sales opportunities.</p>\r\n<p>Zidoff.com is backed byÂ Challydoff Limited. Challydoff Limited is a leading Information Technology Consulting, Services and Software firm. Challydoff creates innovative technological solutions, with unparalleled expertise, derived from her experiences, working on projects that cut across major industries and business sectors. Our primary focus is on excellent service and product delivery.Â </p>\r\n<p>We welcome you to SHOP on Zidoff.com, as your primary source for authentic andÂ heavily discounted goods.</p>', 1, 0, 42, '', '', 0, '35991362173', 1412808982, '::1', '1'),
('5581422066', 'about_us', 'Buying and Selling', '<h3>Buying and Selling</h3>\r\n<hr />\r\n<p>Zidoff global eCommerce platform provides real time marketplace experience, for buyers and sellers. Discounted products are listed by merchants from over 150 countries. These products are well catalogued for buyers worldwide to search for, through our well defined categories and product inventory. Buyers can make more informed choices on merchants and products through available users reviews and ratings. Zidoff provides a secure platform for all financial transactions, logistics and fulfilment for all purchases.</p>\r\n<p>Buyer seeking to get good deals on product prices can visit the&nbsp;Hotdeals. Here they can find&nbsp;very discounted items from various merchants.</p>\r\n<p>Shopping on Zidoff starts with our&nbsp;Search Function. Simply type what you are looking to buy, and you will find numerous products that meets your requirement, with very discounted&nbsp;prices.</p>', 2, 0, 43, '1300130013', '35991362173', 1412808921, '35991362173', 1412808921, '::1', '1'),
('5581440825', 'about_us', 'Customized Store Front & Auctions', '<h3>Customized Store Front &amp; Auctions</h3>\r\n<hr />\r\n<p>Individuals and Merchants,&nbsp;can list their products on Zidoff.com. However we provide businesses with a website-like feature within our platform, which is&nbsp;called&nbsp;the&nbsp;Zidoff Merchants Store Front. With this store Front,&nbsp;sellers can project their companies and products in a more personalized&nbsp;way. They can&nbsp;utilize the URL for business purpose,&nbsp;and advertise their&nbsp;stores&nbsp;on&nbsp;Zidoff Merchant Store&nbsp;Front to their customers.</p>\r\n<p>We also have the&nbsp;Auctions. This is a unique market place for quick sales.&nbsp;Sellers who desire&nbsp;quick sale of their products will feature them in the Auctions.&nbsp;The Auctions allow buyers to place bid for products.&nbsp;The winner is usually the highest bidder.</p>', 3, 0, 44, '1300130013', '35991362173', 1412809109, '35991362173', 1412809109, '::1', '1'),
('5581450226', 'about_us', 'Payment Options', '<h3>Payment Options</h3>\r\n<hr />\r\n<p>Our payment options are easy, secure and highly effective. Buyers and sellers can pay from the comfort of their homes via their MasterCard, Visa, Verve and e-Transact debit / credit cards, or by&nbsp;Bank wire transfer to Zidoff. We&nbsp;provide payment history for all buyers, and&nbsp;constantly update sellers of payment status&nbsp;on&nbsp;purchases, for immediate delivery.</p>', 4, 0, 45, '1300130013', '35991362173', 1412809203, '35991362173', 1412809203, '::1', '1'),
('5581453665', 'about_us', 'Escrow Service', '<h3>Escrow Service</h3>\r\n<hr />\r\n<p>Buyers keep us in business. So we have put together a very strong policy to protect them from any form of fraud from&nbsp;malicious suppliers through our Escrow Service Agreement with all our sellers. Buyer&rsquo;s transactions are kept and protected until they confirm delivery of the ordered item(s), and are satisfied with the item(s). Should there be a problem with the item(s) ordered, the buyer can request for a full refund and return the item(s) to Zidoff.</p>', 5, 0, 46, '1300130013', '35991362173', 1412809237, '35991362173', 1412809237, '::1', '1'),
('5581457318', 'about_us', 'Delivery', '<h3>Delivery</h3>\r\n<hr />\r\n<p>On time delivery is very important to our buyers, to us&nbsp;and to our sellers. Zidoff&nbsp;has partnered with&nbsp;renowned global delivery companies,&nbsp;such as DHL, FedEx and EMS, to meet all our buyers delivery needs, wherever their locations are. So,&nbsp;be very assured your items will get to you just in time.</p>', 6, 0, 47, '1300130013', '35991362173', 1412809274, '35991362173', 1412809274, '::1', '1'),
('5581461213', 'about_us', 'Customer Care Service', '<h3>Customer Care Service</h3>\r\n<hr />\r\n<p>Zidoff customers come first. We have in place a customer relationship management system, to provide us with structured management of our customer&rsquo;s information and collaborations. Through our live chat, support ticketing system, support phone lines and our social media pages, we are positioned to capture our customer&rsquo;s needs, and attend to them appropriately. Our strategic goal, is to provide real time immediate solutions and resolutions to all our users complaints and enquiries.</p>', 7, 0, 48, '1300130013', '35991362173', 1412809313, '35991362173', 1412809313, '::1', '1'),
('5581649967', 'buyers_protection', 'Overview', '<h3>Overview</h3>\r\n<hr />\r\n<p>Buyers keep us in business so we have put together a well thought out policy to protect them from any form of fraud and malicious suppliers through our Escrow service agreement with all our sellers; buyer&rsquo;s payments are kept and protected until they confirm delivery of the ordered item(s) and are satisfied with the item(s), should there be a problem with the item(s) ordered, the buyer can request for a refund and return the item(s) to Zidoff.</p>\r\n<img src="http://www.zidoff.com/engine/files/resource_library/5581574152.jpg" width="100%"/>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>', 1, 0, 49, '1300130013', '35991362173', 1412811200, '35991362173', 1412811200, '::1', '1'),
('5581673366', 'buyers_protection', 'Review All Our Policies', '<h3>Review All Our Policies</h3>\r\n<hr />\r\n<p>We always recommend that buyers review the terms of use of the site, privacy policy, shipping and handling terms, and refund/return policies before placing an order.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>', 2, 0, 50, '1300130013', '35991362173', 1412811434, '35991362173', 1412811434, '::1', '1'),
('5581686652', 'buyers_protection', 'Know the Product Prior to Purchase', '<h3>Know the Product Prior to Purchase</h3>\r\n<hr />\r\n<p>Buyers should thoroughly review the product description provided by the seller. Our platform allows buyers to comment on products and rate the sellers, you can use this tool to know more about a product.</p>\r\n<p>If you plan to order a brand name product (e.g. Adidas &amp; Nike shoes, iPads/iPhones) make sure the supplier has authorized reseller documentation. This will help you confirm the authenticity of the item.</p>\r\n<p>Buyers should check to know the location of the seller because imported goods, will incur taxes or duties in the buyer&rsquo;s country, however our system does additional checks and notifies the buyer during checkout.</p>\r\n<p>It&rsquo;s easy to know a fake product, the prices is often outstandingly lower than similar products so use your better judgment</p>', 3, 0, 51, '1300130013', '35991362173', 1412811567, '35991362173', 1412811567, '::1', '1'),
('5581692915', 'buyers_protection', 'Communicate with Zidoff', '<h3>Communicate with Zidoff</h3>\r\n<hr />\r\n<p>Review the item(s) received to confirm they match the descriptions as stated by the seller, if the item(s) ordered is/are not delivered or you&rsquo;re not satisfied with the product received, you should contact Zidoff immediately</p>', 5, 0, 52, '1300130013', '35991362173', 1412811630, '35991362173', 1412811630, '::1', '1'),
('5581720162', 'selling_on_zidoff', 'Becoming a Seller', '<h3>Overview</h3>\r\n<hr />\r\n<p><img src="http://www.zidoff.com/engine/files/resource_library/5581709514.jpg" alt="" width="100%" /></p>', 1, 0, 53, '', '', 0, '35991362173', 1412812134, '::1', '1'),
('5581725177', 'selling_on_zidoff', 'Probable Fees', '<h3>Probable Fees</h3>\r\n<hr />\r\n<h3>Bank Account Verification Fee</h3>\r\n<div>This fee is to be paid by prospective merchants during the bank account verification process prior to them being able to sell on Zidoff.</div>\r\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h3>Processing Fees</h3>\r\n<div>After sale when we initiate a transfer in order to pay the seller, our bank charges us transaction fees that translates to&nbsp;our processing fees.</div>\r\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>\r\n<h3><strong>Sales Commission</strong></h3>\r\n<div>We charge a small percentage of the stated selling price of items as sales commission. This fee is added to the price of the item stated by the merchant.&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div>', 2, 0, 54, '1300130013', '35991362173', 1412811952, '35991362173', 1412811952, '::1', '1'),
('5581733570', 'selling_on_zidoff', 'Operational Process', '<h3>Operational Process</h3>\r\n<hr />\r\n<img src="http://www.zidoff.com/engine/files/resource_library/5581714116.jpg" width="100%" />', 3, 0, 55, '1300130013', '35991362173', 1412812036, '35991362173', 1412812036, '::1', '1'),
('5581760630', 'getting_started', 'Probable Fees', '<h3>Probable Fees</h3>\r\n<hr />\r\n<div>\r\n<h3>Item Cost</h3>\r\n<div>This is the&nbsp;total cost of merchandise as regard to the selling price stated by the seller.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div>\r\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div>\r\n<h3>Shipping and Handling Fees</h3>\r\n<div>These fees covers the cost of packaging and delivery of items from the seller to the buyer</div>\r\n<div><br />\r\n<h3>Custom Duties</h3>\r\n<div>When buying from a seller in another country, custom duties may apply to dutiable items on arrival into the buyer''s country.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>', 2, 0, 56, '1300130013', '35991362173', 1412812307, '35991362173', 1412812307, '::1', '1'),
('5581776219', 'getting_started', 'Overview', '<h3>Overview</h3>\r\n<hr />\r\n<div>\r\n<img src="http://www.zidoff.com/engine/files/resource_library/5581769034.jpg" width="100%" />\r\n</div>', 1, 0, 57, '1300130013', '35991362173', 1412812463, '35991362173', 1412812463, '::1', '1'),
('6143137378', 'Product_details', 'Payment & Delivery', '<h4>Acceptable Card Types</h4>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>VISA Card</li>\r\n<li>Verve Card</li>\r\n<li>Verve Naira MasterCard</li>\r\n<li>eTranzact Genesis</li>\r\n<li>MasterCard International</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<div><img src="http://www.zidoff.com/engine/files/resource_library/6143387666.png" alt="" width="100%" /></div>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h4>Delivery Process Overview</h4>\r\n<div><img src="http://www.zidoff.com/engine/files/resource_library/6143394615.png" alt="" width="100%" /></div>', 1, 0, 58, '1300130013', '35991362173', 1418429674, '35991362173', 1418432635, '::1', '1'),
('6143139056', 'Product_details', 'Buyers Protection', '<h4>Escrow Service Agreement</h4>\r\n<p>Buyers keep us in business so we have put together a well thought out policy to protect them from any form of fraud and malicious suppliers through our Escrow service agreement with all our sellers; buyer&rsquo;s payments are kept and protected until they confirm delivery of the ordered item(s) and are satisfied with the item(s), should there be a problem with the item(s) ordered, the buyer can request for a refund and return the item(s) to Zidoff.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h4>Refund Procedure</h4>\r\n<div><img src="http://www.zidoff.com/engine/files/resource_library/5581574152.jpg" alt="" width="100%" /></div>', 2, 0, 59, '1300130013', '35991362173', 1418429691, '35991362173', 1418432419, '::1', '1'),
